Class DefaultPaths

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.DefaultPaths

  • public class DefaultPaths
extends Object
    Default model paths for StanfordCoreNLP All these paths point to files distributed with the model jar file (stanford-corenlp-models-*.jar)
